<title>UK: Eidos sets $50 million convertible bond.</title>
<headline>Eidos sets $50 million convertible bond.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following convertible bond was announced by lead manager Deutsche Morgan Grenfell.</p>
<p> BORROWER   EIDOS PLC</p>
<p> AMT	  $50 MLN	COUPON    *6.0-6.5  MATURITY     **2002</p>
<p> TYPE	 CONVERTIBLE  ISS PRICE  *	  PAY DATE  14.APR.97</p>
<p> LISTING    LONDON	 DENOMS (K) 10</p>
<p>NOTES  *TO BE PRICED BY MARCH 17. CONVERSION PREMIUM 22-25 PCT.</p>
<p>	 **NON-CALLABLE FOR TWO YEARS, THEN 140 PCT HURDLE.</p>
</text>
